name: Venom contained
description: Venom- It is a substance that can grant you immense power but at the cost of humanity. A person who comes in contact with this will have a power that will equal that of the legendary Kal Thazard, but only if the person were to remain human. It grants eternal life and power at the cost of Human conscience. They only way to contain this immense power was to divide it and place it with the guardians all across the Globe. So, Human are you ready to be one of the 1000 guardians who are chosen to protect the fate of the Humans??
